  sceneName: 
  audioSource: {fileID: 1781592705}
  sceneManagey: {fileID: 1781592703}
  text:
  - 'After being unable to get a J*b before running out of money, you were tossed
    onto the streets. '
  - 'After landing on the streets it became even harder to land a j*b because who
    would ever want to hire filth like you? '
  - 'Ok, but let''s be real. '
  - 'I am talking to YOU right now, bro. How did you run out of money? What is this,
    some sort of countdown? '
  - 'Now will you try to get all of the endings or just give up here forever, wandering
    the streets looking for scrap?  '
  - '*Homeless Ending Unlocked*'
